OL,3,CZombie knives and crossbow seized
OL,4,Cafter weapons law change
OL,6,FZombie knives and a crossbow have been
OL,7,Fseized in a weapons clamp-down in
OL,8,FSunderland after new legislation
OL,9,Fbrought in to combat offensive weapons.
OL,11,FOfficers have arrested a 55-year-old
OL,12,Fman and a 40-year-old woman on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of possessing an offensive
OL,14,Fweapon.
OL,16,FThey have been released on bail,
OL,17,Fpending further enquiries.
