OL,3,CZombie knives and crossbow seized
OL,4,Cafter weapons law change
OL,6,FThe arrests were made on Wednesday 9
OL,7,FOctober after the police and
OL,8,FSunderland City Council executed a
OL,9,Fwarrant at a property in the Langdale
OL,10,FTerrace area of Hetton-le-Hole
OL,11,Ffollowing reports of anti-social
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,FA number of weapons were seized by
OL,15,Fofficers from the property, including
OL,16,Fnow illegal zombie knives.
