OL,3,CZombie knives and crossbow seized
OL,4,Cafter weapons law change
OL,6,FThe law was changed last month to make
OL,7,Fit illegal to be in possession of a
OL,8,Fzombie-style knife or machete. It is
OL,9,Falso against the law to manufacture,
OL,10,Fimport, sell or supply the items.
OL,12,FBefore the legislation came into
OL,13,Fplace, Northumbria Police - along with
OL,14,Fother forces across the country -
OL,15,Fopened amnesty bins for the weapons
OL,16,Fduring a grace period.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
