OL,3,CZombie knives and crossbow seized
OL,4,Cafter weapons law change
OL,6,FThe legislation defines a 'zombie
OL,7,Fknife' as one with a cutting edge,
OL,8,Fserrated edge, and images or words, on
OL,9,Fthe blade or handle, which suggest it
OL,10,Fwill be used for the purposes of
OL,11,Fviolence.
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police knife crime lead
OL,14,FChief Superintendent Joanne Park-
OL,15,FSimmons said: "This is a great piece
OL,16,Fof work by all involved and shows our
OL,17,Fcontinued commitment to seizing these
OL,18,Fdangerous weapons.
