OL,3,CZombie knives and crossbow seized
OL,4,Cafter weapons law change
OL,6,F"As we have sadly learned, knife crime
OL,7,Fcan have devastating consequences in
OL,8,Four communities.
OL,10,F"That's why it's important that people
OL,11,Fcontinue to share information with us,
OL,12,Fso we can take appropriate action to
OL,13,Fhelp keep you safe.
OL,15,F"If you know of anyone who is
OL,16,Funlawfully in possession of zombie-
OL,17,Fstyle knives or machetes, we urge you
OL,18,Fto come forward with information as
OL,19,Fsoon as possible."
